{"tid":1543271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家推爆佢，唔係31/8真相冇架喇","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T06:38:05.000Z","uid":307288,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae16a703a4910745d3f0929b0d9fb611cec543e1","tid":1543271,"uid":307288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:33:30.000Z","msg":"從 721 進階到 831<br />\n不能再這樣混下去<br />\n<br />\n⭐⭐⭐  重要  ⭐⭐⭐<br />\n<br />\n最快兩日，港鐵就可以刪除 831 晚太子站cctv，到時你、被防暴圍毆嘅抗爭者同乘客，唔會再攞得返公道。<br />\n<br />\n之前講過無論你係受傷定受驚，都可以向香港警察或港鐵提出民事訴訟，申請要法庭強制命令港鐵交出 831 當晚既CCTV。 有法庭命令，港鐵唔交就係藐視法庭！  😡<br />\n<br />\n成班義務律師大狀已經準備就緒！ <br />\n受害人唔使怕有咩隱憂，例如自爆、金錢、時間，義務律師會同你傾咗先，商量吓再決定告唔告，一切內容絕對保密。🤐👌<br />\n<br />\n港鐵每7-28日就會清一次cctv，換言之我哋最快得返兩日去揾證據，時間一過，在場所有人受到嘅傷害、屈辱，將會永遠石沉大海，而毆打你哋嘅武裝分子繼續逍遙法外，無後果地打壓香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n就喺呢兩日，你可以選擇還 831 傷者一個公道，將黑警暴行昭告天下。<br />\n<br />\n⚠⚠⚠ 就算你唔喺現場，都請你幫手轉發廣傳，whatsapp，Facebook，IG等，比在場者見到為止。⚠⚠⚠<br />\n<br />\n831 受害者請盡快聯絡以下團體：<br />\n<br />\n1. 星火: 9819 0979 <br />\n2. 民陣: 6549 9452 <br />\n3. 民權: 9463 2945<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenSchumer/status/1169325161272795142?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenSchumer%2Fstatus%2F1169325161272795142%3Fs%3D09&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=f5238012\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenSchumer%2Fstatus%2F1169325161272795142%3Fs%3D09&h=52b590f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenSchumer/status/1169325161272795142?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1168938131212689408?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1168938131212689408%3Fs%3D09&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=27327542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1168938131212689408%3Fs%3D09&h=756529dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t